		<table class="table">
			<tr>
				<th>Title of Invention</th>
				<td><h1 style="font-size:large;">&quot;A METHOD FOR STORING AUDIO-CENTERED INFORMATION WITH A MULTI-LEVEL TABLE-OF-CONTENTENTS (TOC) MECHANISM WITH ONE MASTER-TOCS FOR VARIOUS AUDIO FORMATS, A DEVICE FOR USE WITH SUCH MECHANISM AND A UNITARY STORAGE MEDIUM CONTAINING SUCH MECHANISM</h1></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<th>Abstract</th>
				<td>Audio information is stored on a unitary storage medium with a Table-of-Contents (TOC) mechanism for therein specifying an actual configuration of various audio items on the medium, In particular, one or more Sub-TOCs are each assigned to a respective different audio format. A single Master-TOC is provided for specifically pointing to each Sub-TOC.</td>
			</tr>
		</table>

